This paper deals with natural language processing and language understanding, which are closely related to the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques to estimate indirect anaphora, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of a case frame dictionary, which is related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Natural Language Processing (cs.NE).
